creator: CBRE Inc.
descriptionHtml:
The official Flow & Glow event app is your ticket to unlock the very best of what’s happening in Sydney’s Wynyard neighbourhood on May 26-27.

By day, enjoy inspirational content in partnership with TEDxSydney, an artists’ market and instaworthy art installations.

By night, visit the neighbourhood bars and restaurants and listen to a line-up of DJs, all while partying in the glow of the art.

Download the app to learn more about the program of free, experiential activities, including the full schedule, line-up and location details.

You can also access exclusive offers from Wynyard’s favourite bars, restaurants and retailers during the event.

The Flow & Glow app is powered by CBRE’s Host technology.
